### Build index by path
POST {{host}}/data/index
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

path=uploads%2Fkeec101.pdf&subject=Economics&chapter=1&chunk_size=1200&chunk_overlap=200&model=all-MiniLM-L6-v2

### Build index by uploading
POST {{host}}/data/index
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="subject"

Economics
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="chapter"

1
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="keec101.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./keec101.pdf
--boundary--

